git init   -  initialize repository
create files and folders using vim
git status -  status of file
git diff  -  to tack difference
git add .  -  add all files
git commit -m 'message' <filename>  -  commit(save) with message
git show git_id
git diff --cached 
git log -   shows all commits
git reset <filename>   -  to go to previous content
git checkout filename  -  to discard changes that you made


